# STANDALONE feedback-triage surface (issue #59): a clean, extensionless alias for
# the second build entry. Real static files (/feedback-admin.html itself, /assets/*,
# /data/*, /sw.js) are served by Pages BEFORE these rules; this rewrite only handles
# the extensionless path. It is deliberately NOT linked from the app — reachable by
# direct URL only. Must precede the SPA catch-all so it isn't swallowed by it.
/feedback-admin    /feedback-admin.html    200

# SPA fallback: serve index.html for any path that isn't a real static file.
# (Cloudflare Pages serves existing files — /assets/*, /data/*, /sw.js — first.)
/*    /index.html    200
